OPEN SOURCE COMPONENTS
----------------------

The following components are licensed under the Apache License 2.0 and are
fully open source:

- crypto-core/ (EnvCrypto.psm1, WindowsHelloAuth.cs, encryption logic)
- cli/ (scrt CLI tool and all commands)
- npm-package/ (CLI distribution package)

See LICENSE-APACHE for full terms of those components.

This dual-licensing ensures you can audit the cryptographic code that protects
your secrets while allowing us to sustain development of the desktop application.


ENCRYPTION DISCLAIMER
---------------------

This software uses AES-256 encryption and Windows Hello authentication.

NO WARRANTY is provided that encryption will be unbreakable or that data will
be recoverable if:

- Master key is lost
- Windows Hello authentication fails
- Hardware or software failures occur

You are solely responsible for:

- Backing up your master encryption key
- Testing the recovery process before relying on the system
- Maintaining backups of important data


